{"tid":1354753,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無畏無懼！所有人同我入元朗，策略／文宣方向","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:37:27.000Z","uid":257020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc28af11ecf747323dc42564572ba1678bb3eb3","tid":1354753,"uid":257020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"我希望做到有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">200萬 甚至300萬</span></strong>和理非一齊去光復元朗大遊行<br />\n我瞓得好差，個頭好痛，好想瞓多陣，但諗到啲方向希望大家可以睇睇！<br />\n策略／文宣方向大致上都係呼應細良哥尋日嗰集：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QbJTdHbdGIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQbJTdHbdGIU&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=9d4b9088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QbJTdHbdGIU</a><br />\n如果有時間睇晒佢，我覺得有好多啟示<br />\n<br />\n最重要係一定要入元朗<br />\n但<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好衝擊</span></span></strong><br />\n細良哥甚至話唔洗帶裝備<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但我覺得都要少少保護自己</span><br />\n唔衝的話就要智取<br />\n首先，我覺得人數好有用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">200/300萬大軍嚟到，我唔信佢敢做啲咩</span></span><br />\n佢哋都係收錢先做嘢咋<br />\n<br />\n第二，絲打出動！<br />\n見好多巴打分析唔好燒村燒祠堂，我覺得都好合理，容易走火！<br />\n先前見到有位巴打提議<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用Ｍ巾</span></span><br />\n佢哋好避忌，或者用其他佢哋會避之則吉嘅嘢！！<br />\n我認為可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用嚟痴落佢條祠堂，痴落條村唔同地方</span></span><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><em>甚至整個Ｍ巾連儂牆</em></ins></span></span></strong></strong><br />\n試諗吓成條村都痴滿Ｍ巾，俾傳媒影到相揚晒，佢哋仲有冇面？<br />\n另外，萬一前線有啲衝突，俾人打<br />\n或者可以掉Ｍ巾守（最紅事先塗定啲好油先）<br />\n總知就務求令佢哋見到就閃開<br />\n唔該大家，全民馬上去掃Ｍ巾（巴打要突破心房啊！）<br />\n<br />\n第三，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好俾二哥鄧柄強上位坐正</span></span><br />\n佢先前係元朗指揮官，仲有幾個月就坐正！<br />\n細良哥同其他人都有分析過，由6月都依家，係鄧柄強主導警方策略<br />\n之前都有錄音流出，佢好鼓勵前線打記者，唔好俾人影到就得<br />\n可想而知佢係十分心狼手辣<br />\n今次鄉黑合作更加係佢策劃/包疪<br />\n大家試吓新口號<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要二哥鄧柄強，串聯鄉黑好無良</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">麻煩文宣幫手整圖</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四，追擊石鏡泉<br />\n關於呢樣嘢，我早前開過post<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《追擊石鏡泉，罷買罷睇經濟日報旗下產品》</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dowrcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dowrcT</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該文宣幫手整圖</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多先<br />\n打咗好耐，請大家俾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認同請分享"},{"pid":"11553a62ab8977d581ad7f781332a295567aab0f","tid":1354753,"uid":257020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩其他巴打幫手分析邊幾條村/祠堂可以入</span>"},{"pid":"db1e5eb8f875796299215143c14d85b942108f1e","tid":1354753,"uid":110870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n一個時間 光復元朗 黑衣圍城<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344965</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c4bd90ccd7f2423f934522fe9a45504616128c83","tid":1354753,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"你當m巾係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2368975ccbd0f6d364f4e6cc0f1dc452a0c4eb28","tid":1354753,"uid":257020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4bd90ccd7f2423f934522fe9a45504616128c83","tid":1354753,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"你當m巾係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4252656d3e4a2ed1d33a68e044ef96fb2142ccdb","tid":1354753,"uid":257020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"78140d5d2e8c6d0bee108c2a5531e7d14cbef290","tid":1354753,"uid":257020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}